node.text: Ella es una maldicion🥀 — Not to eat my own pompis but I’m really happy with how far Karla has come. She had her very first photoshoot and best believe she was at her fulllll perra potential. For those who don’t know, Karla is my alter ego who basically created the baddest perra. Before Karla, it was just Louie. I was shy, confused, scared to be myself, scared of others opinions, pero when Karla was unleashed… it was over ssstupidas. Karla has shaped me to who I am today and helped me not give a fff about others opinions. To everyone who has shown Karla and I love and support thank you!! It’ll all about having fun and making sure YOU ARE HAPPY!💜
